{"about_the_game":"&quot;<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Brew, Spill, Repeat!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the chaotic world of Clumsy Coffee Simulator, where you play as an ambitious yet hilariously clumsy barista! Serve up coffee orders with precision, or at least try to, as you navigate through a bustling caf\u00e9 filled with unexpected challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your caf\u00e9 to reflect your unique style. Whether it's adding a new lamp or rearranging furniture, you can give your place a personal touch that stands out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991850/extras/StylizingThePlace.gif?t=1736127956\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your shelves stocked and organized, ensuring you always have what you need on hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991850/extras/StoringItems.gif?t=1736127956\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with a variety of customers, taking their orders and attempting to fulfill them with accuracy. The more precise you are, the better tips you'll earn, helping you progress through the game and unlock new recipes and tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991850/extras/TakingOrders.gif?t=1736127956\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the art of making perfect recipes, which you can find detailed in the menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991850/extras/Cusomizing_Menus.gif?t=1736127956\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your caf\u00e9 to accommodate more customers and offer new exciting features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragrap